'''巴雅塔斯'''是位於[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]][[奎松市|奎松市]]的一個社區，所在之處有一個佔地50英畝的[[垃圾堆填區|垃圾堆填區]]，因而亦被稱為「第二個[[斯莫基山|斯莫基山]]」。<ref>{{cite book|last=Leon-Guerrero|first=Anna|title=Social problems: community, policy, and social action|year=2010|publisher=Pine Forge Press|location=Thousand Oaks, Calif.|isbn=1412988055|page=413|url=http://books.google.com.ph/books?id=SHsrnuoN-ysC&pg=PA413&dq=payatas+second+smokey+mountain&hl=en&sa=X&ei=RhWcUeiNF460iQeci4GIDA&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=payatas%20second%20smokey%20mountain&f=false|edition=3rd ed.|access-date=2013-06-13|archive-date=2019-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107062633/https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=SHsrnuoN-ysC&pg=PA413&dq=payatas+second+smokey+mountain&hl=en&sa=X&ei=RhWcUeiNF460iQeci4GIDA&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=payatas%20second%20smokey%20mountain&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2000年7月11日發生了一次[[山泥傾瀉|山泥傾瀉]]般的垃圾倒塌事件，官方數字聲稱218人死亡及300人失蹤。<ref>{{cite book|last=(Habitat)|first=United Nations Centre for Human Settlements|title=Cities in a globalizing world|year=2001|publisher=Earthscan|location=London [u.a.]|isbn=1853838063|page=xxvi|url=http://books.google.com.ph/books?id=Kk8f9E-Hcj0C&pg=PR26&dq=payatas&hl=en&sa=X&ei=YRGcUaL-CYujiAew4YHICw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=payatas&f=false|edition=1. publ. in the UK and USA.|access-date=2013-06-13|archive-date=2019-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023104103/https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=Kk8f9E-Hcj0C&pg=PR26&dq=payatas&hl=en&sa=X&ei=YRGcUaL-CYujiAew4YHICw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=payatas&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>依照[[拾荒者|拾荒者]]的要求，災難後數月堆填區已經繼續運作，迄今仍然是菲律賓最大的開放式垃圾場。當局採取了一些措施改善垃圾場的安全，包括：垃圾堆放的角度已經由從前的70度大幅降低到40度，14歲以下的兒童禁止入內拾荒，垃圾分解發出的[[甲烷|甲烷]]亦得到收集並用以[[發電|發電]]。<ref>[http://zh-tw.apocalisselaica.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=158603%3Afilippine-alla-discarica-di-payatas-metano-diventa-elettricit%C3%A0%C2%A0&catid=223%3Aambiente&Itemid=219 菲律賓：在給巴雅塔斯垃圾填埋場沼氣轉化為電能]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}《TMNews》2013年4月3日</ref>

2010 年 12 月，垃圾填埋場關閉。<ref>{{cite web |title=Quezon City Local Government - Background (Domestic Solid Waste) |url=https://www.quezoncity.gov.ph/index.php/about-the-city-government/background |website=Quezon City Official Website |publisher=Quezon City Government |accessdate=23 September 2019 |archive-date=16 June 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616062013/https://www.quezoncity.gov.ph/index.php/about-the-city-government/background |url-status=live }}</ref> 2011 年 1 月，在舊露天垃圾場附近建立了一個具有更嚴格廢物管理政策的單獨垃圾填埋場。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ranada |first1=Pia |title=Time ticking for Payatas landfill |url=https://www.rappler.com/nation/52307-payatas-landfill-end-contract |accessdate=23 September 2019 |work=Rappler |date=6 March 2014 |archive-date=23 September 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923031337/https://www.rappler.com/nation/52307-payatas-landfill-end-contract |url-status=live }}</ref> 該垃圾場於 2017 年 12 月關閉，以便根據環境管理局 2017 年 8 月 2 日發布的命令，審查垃圾場運營商 IPM Environmental Services 的環境合規證書。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Roxas |first1=Pathricia Ann |title=Environmentalists hail closure of Payatas dumpsite |url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/920737/environmentalists-hail-closure-of-payatas-dumpsite |accessdate=23 September 2019 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=August 6, 2017 |archive-date=23 September 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923031337/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/920737/environmentalists-hail-closure-of-payatas-dumpsite |url-status=live }}</ref>

